outputs.output_descr: The project provides the country office with seed money to support activities linked to programme and project development in Mauritius and Seychelles outside the core resources. It is executed directly by the UNDP and helps the office to respond positively to adhoc request from government for key initiatives mostly linked to policy development and advocacy.
